11. 🧠 SYSTEM INTEGRITY STATEMENT

The PanjoCoin system is defined as:

A deterministic multi-contract financial system where supply, staking, liquidity, vesting, and governance must always satisfy a closed set of mathematical invariants under all valid execution paths.

12. 🏁 FINAL CONCLUSION

This invariant system guarantees:

✔ Supply cannot be corrupted
✔ Liquidity cannot be bypassed
✔ Staking cannot be exploited externally
✔ Vesting cannot be accelerated
✔ Governance cannot be centralized
✔ System state remains deterministic

